<h2 style="text-align: center;">FAQ’s</h2>
<p><strong>Why was Esprit Ski holidays retired?</strong></p>
<p>In February 2024 we made the extremely difficult decision to make the 2023/24 season Esprit’s last winter. Moving forward, we will place our focus, and our passion for skiing into Inghams.</p>
<p><strong>Can I book childcare for my child with Inghams?</strong></p>
<p>We do not offer any childcare services operated by Inghams, however we do work with a number of brilliant family friendly partners in our resorts that offer childcare options which you can read more about <a data-udi="umb://document/e0f33c40be46416cbb547a6f9e327b61" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0f33c40be46416cbb547a6f9e327b61}" title="Ski holidays with childcare options">here</a>. As well as dedicated ski schools offering children’s classes and optional lunch add-ons. You can find out more <a data-udi="umb://document/e4565aae9d704cf59edeca5aba507d16" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e4565aae9d704cf59edeca5aba507d16}" title="Ski Lessons">here</a> or you can call our team who will be able to give you some recommendations.</p>
<p><strong>Does Inghams offer any child discounts? </strong></p>
<p>Yes, view our Child Discounts Special Offers page to view all offers <a data-udi="umb://document/db7a2008a7c84902a4dc5ab441016bf6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/db7a2008a7c84902a4dc5ab441016bf6}" title="2024/25 Discounted child places">here</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Can I book ski lessons for my family with Inghams?</strong></p>
<p>Yes, when booking a ski holiday with Inghams, you can opt to add <a data-udi="umb://document/e4565aae9d704cf59edeca5aba507d16" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e4565aae9d704cf59edeca5aba507d16}" title="Ski Lessons">ski lessons</a>.</p>
<p><strong>What family skiing holiday options does Inghams offer?</strong></p>
<p>We offer a variety of resorts that are family friendly, read more about these resorts <a data-udi="umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875}" title="Family Ski Holidays">here</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Why book with Inghams?</strong></p>
<p>Bringing you the same level care and knowledge as out sister company Esprit, Inghams is with you all the way - before, during and after your holiday our teams are here to support and guide you. This includes a Resort Representative, one of our team members who is knowledgeable in the activity, resort and country you have chosen for your holiday - they will be available to answer any questions during your holiday. With 90 years of expertise you are <a data-udi="umb://document/1c0238bc20ce42999f3d8bd087aa32d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1c0238bc20ce42999f3d8bd087aa32d1}" title="In Safe Hands">in safe hands</a>. <a data-udi="umb://document/1e437ab1de9c402abf63da580ffe1715" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1e437ab1de9c402abf63da580ffe1715}" title="About Us">View more about Inghams</a>.</p>
<p><strong>What are Inghams' Choice properties?</strong></p>
<p>Inghams' Choice properties are hand selected accommodation options that our Inghams experts highly recommend. View all Inghams' Choice properties <a data-udi="umb://document/49b9c2d67d104ca3879a39351d601ab0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/49b9c2d67d104ca3879a39351d601ab0}" title="Inghams Choice Accommodation">here</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Can I use my Esprit Loyalty Discount with Inghams?</strong></p>
<p>Yes, 5% off the 2nd to 4th holiday you book with us or 10% off your 5th holiday and this discount can now be applied to an -<br /><a data-udi="umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e}" title="Ski Holidays">Inghams Ski holiday</a> for ski season 2024/25<br /><a data-udi="umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416" href="/{localLink:umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416}" title="Walking Holidays">Inghams Walking holiday</a> for summer 2024<br /><a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Inghams Lapland holiday</a> for winter 2024/25<br />In addition, you can also use your discount on our sister brand, <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.santaslapland.com/" target="_blank" title="Santa's Lapland">Santa's Lapland</a> for a 2024 holiday.</p>
<p>Your loyalty bonus must be registered at time of booking and cannot be added subsequently. To claim your discount, please call 01483 319 514 and quote your last Esprit booking reference.</p>
<p><em>*Please note: These discounts apply to adults only, and are calculated off the basic adult price, not including any flight or room supplements, ski packs, childcare and other extras. Discounts apply to full priced flight inclusive holidays only.</em></p>
